    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have learned to find even the smallest gaps in your opponents' guards, being able to exploit their shortcomings.</p><p> Beginning at 11th level, when you would make an attack with your hammer or nail you can spend 3 cursed energy to ignore any penalties imposed on the attack roll and ignore resistance.</p><p> When Magnified: You treat immunity as resistance and any attack roll penalties are now turned into bonuses.</p><p></p>",
